'''[[Israel]]''' competed at the '''[[1998 Winter Olympics]]''' in [[Nagano, Nagano|Nagano]], [[Japan]].
The Israeli delegation included 3 figure skaters. [[Michael Shmerkin]] competed in the men's event, [[Galit Chait]] and [[Sergei Sakhnovski]] competed in [[ice dancing]].<ref>[https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/countries/ISR/winter/1998/ Israel at the 1998 Nagano Winter Games] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090523065603/http://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/countries/ISR/winter/1998/ |date=2009-05-23 }}</ref>
