==Personal life== Casciaro works as a shipping agent at Cory Brothers in Gibraltar.<ref>{{cite news|title=Gibraltar v Poland: Starting XIs by professional occupation|url=http://i100.independent.co.uk/article/gibraltar-v-poland-starting-xis-by-professional-occupation--l13c2aPE4g|accessdate=9 September 2014|publisher=The Independent}}</ref> His brothers [[Lee Casciaro|Lee]] and [[Ryan Casciaro|Ryan]] have also played with Gibraltar's national side.<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.marca.com/en/2015/03/30/en/football/international_football/1427666595.html |title=A policeman goes down in Gibraltar history |newspaper=[[Marca (newspaper)|Marca]] |date=30 Mar 2015 |accessdate=9 Oct 2016}}</ref>
