'''Lejre Stadion''' is a football stadium that belongs to Danish [[Association football]] club [[FC Lejre]]. Lejre Stadion has a [[Seating capacity|capacity]] of 5,300 and was built in 1989. The match with the highest attendance was in 2008, when 4,908 spectators saw the match between [[FC Lejre]] and [[FC Nordsjælland]].

