{{Infobox stadium | stadium_name = Mestský futbalový štadión Bardejov | image = | caption = | location = [[Bardejov]], [[Slovakia]] | coordinates = {{coord|49|17.36|N|21|16.34|E|region:SK-BL_type:landmark|display=inline,title}} | opened = 1966 | renovated = 2012, 2015-16 | expanded = | closed = | operator = [[Partizán Bardejov]] | surface = Grass | tenants = [[Partizán Bardejov]] | capacity = 3,040<ref>[http://www.bardejov.sk/mesto/kultura-a-sport/sport/sportoviska http://www.bardejov.sk/mesto/kultura-a-sport/sport/sportoviska] 07.02.2012, bardejov.sk</ref> | dimensions = 110 x 65 m }}
'''Mestský štadión Bardejov''' is a multi-use [[stadium]] in [[Bardejov]], [[Slovakia]]. It is currently used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and is the home ground of [[Partizán Bardejov]]. The stadium holds 2,612 people. In 2012, has hosted the final match of [[2011–12 Slovak Cup|Slovak Cup]].<ref>[http://sport.aktuality.sk/c/130345/msk-zilina-prvykrat-v-historii-vitazom-slovenskeho-pohara/ MŠK Žilina prvýkrát v histórii víťazom Slovenského pohára!] 08.05.2012, sport.aktuality.sk</ref>
== Reconstruction== In 2015 began reconstruction of the stadium for 4,000 spectators. The estimated cost is €1.5 million.<ref>http://www.profutbal.sk/ligy/svk2/clanok199838-V_Bardejove_vyrasta_uplne_novy_futbalovy_stanok_hrat_sa_na_nom_bude_uz_o_rok.htm</ref>
