{{Infobox country at games | NOC = THA | NOCname = [[National Olympic Committee of Thailand]] | oldcode = | year = 1970 | date = | games = Asian Games | location = [[Bangkok]] | competitors = | sports = | flagbearer = | officials = | gold = 9 | silver = 17 | bronze = 13 | rank = 3 | appearances = auto | seealso = | website = {{URL|www.olympicthai.or.th/eng}}&nbsp;{{en icon}} {{th icon}} }}
'''[[Thailand]]''' was the host nation for the '''[[1970 Asian Games]]''' in [[Bangkok]] on 24 October to 4 September 1978. Thailand ended the games at 39 overall medals including 9 gold medals.
